HEADWORD: Adoptionist
<hw>A*dop"tion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld> <def>One
of a sect which maintained that Christ was the Son of God not by nature
but by adoption.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

